Package: winetop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: htop for Wine prefixes
 Native CLI/TUI to monitor and stop Wine, Proton, Lutris, Heroic, and
 Bottles sessions. Groups processes by WINEPREFIX / Steam AppId, shows
 resource usage, and supports a safe kill ladder (reaper, wineserver -k).
